<ChannelTradeLayout
  title="AI Instagram DMs for Extension Specialists | Rapid Receptionist"
  description={`AI Instagram DMs for UK extension specialists. Converts followers inspired by kitchen-diner transformations and build-progress reels into extension consultations. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
  canonicalUrl="/extension-specialists/ai-instagram-dms/"
  channelName="AI Instagram DMs"
  tradeName="Extension Specialist"
  tradeNamePlural="Extension Specialists"
  tradeSlug="extension-specialists"
  headline="AI Instagram DMs for Extension Specialist Companies"
  accentWord="Extension Specialist"
  subhead="Your latest reel is a split-screen reveal — the left side showing a narrow, dated 1970s kitchen with textured wallpaper and a single window; the right showing the same house after a 5-metre rear extension with bi-fold doors, a skylight lantern, an island with waterfall worktop, and herringbone oak flooring. Sixty thousand views. A homeowner DMs: 'Obsessed with this. Our kitchen is basically the before photo. We want to do exactly this. Can you come and look at ours?' You are on site, supervising the pouring of a ground-floor slab at a wraparound extension. Without AI DMs, the message waits until the evening. With it, the homeowner gets an instant response, shares photos of her current kitchen, and your lead — 1970s kitchen, rear extension, bi-folds, lantern, island — is waiting when you clean up."
  scenario="It is 9:45pm on a Saturday. An interior designer in Summertown is planning a kitchen project for a client who lives in a Victorian terrace in North Oxford. The house has a long, narrow kitchen with a lean-to utility room on the back. The plan is to demolish the lean-to, extend the full width of the rear elevation by three metres, and create a contemporary kitchen-dining space with a parapet flat roof, structural glazing, and level-threshold sliding doors. She has been browsing Instagram for extension specialists with a contemporary aesthetic and finds your account. Your portfolio matches her vision — clean lines, precise detailing, quality materials. She DMs: 'Beautiful work. I am designing a rear extension for a Victorian terrace in OX2 — full-width to the boundary, 3m projection, parapet flat roof, structural glazing panel, and level threshold sliding doors. Budget around £75,000 for the build. Would you be interested in quoting? I can send the architect's GA drawings and specification.' Without AI Instagram DMs, you see the message Sunday lunchtime. She DM'd two other extension specialists; one replied at 10pm with examples of similar Victorian terrace extensions. With AI Instagram DMs, the reply arrives at 9:46pm: 'Thank you — Victorian terrace extensions with contemporary design are among our favourite projects. We would love to review the drawings. Could you share the GA plans and specification? One of our team will call you early next week to discuss the scope and arrange a site visit.' She sends the architect's drawings and her contact details. Monday morning you open the lead: Victorian terrace, OX2, full-width rear extension, 3m projection, parapet flat roof, structural glazing, £75k budget, interior designer contact, GA drawings attached. You call at 9am and discuss the programme — start date, party wall timeline, and material lead times."
  benefits={benefits}
  faqs={faqs}
  channelPageUrl="/construction-trades/ai-instagram-dms/"
  tradePageUrl="/extension-specialists/ai-receptionist/"
  ctaHeadline="Turn Kitchen Reveal Reels into Extension Consultations"
  ctaSubhead={`A split-screen transformation reel earns sixty thousand views. AI Instagram DMs converts every enquiry into a lead with dimensions, planning, and design intent. Add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month.`}
/>
